what git is (so uk before u download it):

developers/ companies use GITHUB to share code files and save code files online. 

GIT is a command line interface (eg in ur mac terminal) tool that allows you to write commands to directly interact with code files on GITHUB. 

on the surface level: GIT allows you to pull (download) and push (upload) files to the code files stored on GITHUB.

Background:
The Sustainability Startathon Country Round is a pre-event to the Annual ASEAN-China-India Youth Leadership Summit held in Singapore. The ASEAN-China-India Youth Leadership Summit 2024 addresses the most pressing sustainability challenges of our time.

Challenge area #1 - Smart Cities ​🌆
Challenge area #2 - Waste management ​​​🗑
Challenge area #3 - Energy demand​ 🔋

In recognition of the outstanding efforts and achievements of 
the winning teams, Top winning teams will be awarded 
scholarships to attend the

text.text: ASEAN-China-India Youth Leadership Summit in Singapore

text_entities.text: ASEAN-CHINA-INDIA: Youth Leadership Summit 2024——The SUSTAINABILITY STARTATHON｜Prioritizing and Integrating AI in building a resilient city

Background:
The Sustainability Startathon Country Round is a pre-event to the Annual ASEAN-China-India Youth Leadership Summit held in Singapore. The ASEAN-China-India Youth Leadership Summit 2024 addresses the most pressing sustainability challenges of our time.

Challenge area #1 - Smart Cities ​🌆
Challenge area #2 - Waste management ​​​🗑
Challenge area #3 - Energy demand​ 🔋

In recognition of the outstanding efforts and achievements of 
the winning teams, Top winning teams will be awarded 
scholarships to attend the
ASEAN-China-India Youth Leadership Summit in Singapore

If everything goes into the right direction, you can eventually date with someone, which is the most important thing for campus life (much more important than calculus).

messages.text:
When I’m not studying, I’m probably dancing; my involvement in NUS’ dance scene has deepened my passion for genres like breaking and hip hop, which originated in the US. Immersing myself in their street dance culture would be an amazing opportunity, with a dynamic community that promises both skill growth and rich cultural exchange. Similarly, the University of California (UC) boasts a myriad of clubs and activities, offering a vibrant student life where I can further experience the dance scene and connect with those that share my passion. UC also offers the unique opportunity to engage with a wide range of perspectives through an ethnically diverse community, allowing me to embrace new cultural experiences and build meaningful connections.

As someone deeply fascinated by the beauty of mathematics, I am drawn to UC’s renowned math programs and the chance to delve into innovative research and specialized courses at San Diego and Berkeley. Their approach of interactive and discussion-based learning, exploring concepts through collaborative hands-on experiences, is a fresh change from Singapore's exam-centric, lecture-based style I’m used to, allowing for deeper engagement of mathematical theories and applications, while sharpening essential skills like communication and problem-solving. By stepping out of my comfort zone beyond academics and experiencing a new educational environment, I hope to gain fresh perspectives that will enrich both my academic journey and future career.

messages.text:
Dear CAPTains, 

We have received a report of a potential trespasser (ie non CAPT resident) in the College at about 10 pm today. 

Based on the statements gathered so far, it is likely that he is not a CAPT resident who is not accompanied by a CAPTain.

The person was wearing white T shirt and shorts, black specs holding a headphone, black jacket and a portable fan.

The RL team has called CES and they have arrived. We have requested for a sweep of all female toilets. In the mean time, please do not use the toilets. Once we have the all clear, I will follow up with a message. 

We are now in the midst of gathering information to piece the info together, so that CES can investigate. If you have information or have seen the person, please come to L1 lobby to help us piece the statements together.

Thanks for being vigilant and please wait for further updates.

Dr Toh 
CAPT Director of Resident Life.

text:
We are excited to announce that registration is now open for the NUS Alphathon 2024, a competition that challenges participants to build "Alphas" using historical market data on WorldQuancht BRAIN’s simulation platform. This is a fantastic opportunity to test your quantitative finance skills and compete for exciting rewards!

Key Details:
Event: NUS Alphathon 2024
Registration Period: 23 Sep - 6 Nov 2024
Competition Period: 17 Oct - 6 Nov 2024

Stipend: Top performers may be eligible for a one-time stipend from a pool of USD 3,000!*

Top 3: USD 1,000 / 700 / 400
Top 4-5: USD 200 each
Top 6-10: USD 100 each

Don’t miss your chance to participate in this event and potentially earn a Research Consultant opportunity with WorldQuant BRAIN.

How to Join:
Register for the Competition:
